com.github.jhanne82.documenttree

Class DocumentNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jhanne82.documenttree.DocumentNode<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the elements of terms describing the document.

    public class DocumentNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic representation of a DocumentNode. The DocumentNode can be used as node element within a binary tree and keeps references to the parent, and both child elements.
